Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.77,0:00:57.64,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroi kaze
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.64,0:01:01.95,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I want it to be a crush, then love
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.64,0:01:01.95,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nee koi ni natte ai ni natte
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.95,0:01:03.48,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to spread my wings
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.95,0:01:03.48,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hane hirogetai
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.48,0:01:07.35,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, take the good things and the bad
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.48,0:01:07.35,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nee ii koto mo warui koto mo
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.35,0:01:09.29,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Add them all together
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.35,0:01:09.29,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Subete tashite
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.29,0:01:13.83,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Divide it by two and live well
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.29,0:01:13.83,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ni de watte umaku ikite
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.83,0:01:21.76,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to transcend time
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.83,0:01:21.76,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Toki o koetai
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.41,0:01:35.11,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Je mi ľúto, že ti tým spôsobím problémy...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.18,0:01:38.24,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...ale svoj názor nezmením.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.55,0:01:40.78,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.95,0:01:43.59,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Už nie sme deti.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.59,0:01:45.58,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vystačíš si s Fujisaki.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.02,0:01:47.25,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo tým chceš povedať?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.19,0:01:50.02,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Premýšľal som,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.53,0:01:53.40,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,myslím, že sa nechcem\Nnaďalej živiť hudbou.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.77,0:01:56.43,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No tak, len sme začali!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.43,0:01:58.30,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ako to môžeš vedieť?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.70,0:02:02.77,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To, že nad tým takto premýšľam...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.77,0:02:04.64,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...znamená, že sa na túto prácu nehodím.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.82,0:02:18.95,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Počuj,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.36,0:02:21.29,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,spomínaš, čo si mi povedal...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.29,0:02:23.09,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...keď som bol vtedy na dne?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.09,0:02:25.89,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Povedal si, "Tvoj spev je najlepší\Nv Japonsku! Musíš si veriť".
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.43,0:02:27.70,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Preto som...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.70,0:02:28.79,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To Yuki.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.34,0:02:33.91,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ten, kto ťa postavil na nohy, som nebol ja.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.91,0:02:35.46,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale Yuki.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.31,0:02:40.80,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Budeš v poriadku, nepotrebuješ ma.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.95,0:02:50.05,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.79,0:02:54.23,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ja... myslím, že som\Nnaňho začal žiarliť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.69,0:02:59.29,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vždy sme boli ako priatelia,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.76,0:03:01.23,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ale predsalen som zamilovaný.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.87,0:03:04.70,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?! To je prúser!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.30,0:03:08.11,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sme dobrí priatelia,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.11,0:03:10.38,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,pracovali sme vždy spolu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.38,0:03:12.24,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cením si tvojích citov, ale...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.24,0:03:14.08,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miluje Yukiho.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.51,0:03:17.48,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aj po tom, čo zrušili svoje zasnúbenie.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.65,0:03:21.18,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ty minuleš...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.49,0:03:23.61,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...Ayaku?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.01,0:03:42.20,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kto je tam?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.88,0:03:54.78,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chýbal si mi, Yuki!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.55,0:03:57.46,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,V tomto kostýme ma nespoznajú!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.46,0:03:59.01,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tie otravné média.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.72,0:04:01.52,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Na to, že si ho vymyslel ty,\Nje to dobrý nápad.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.06,0:04:03.08,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Myslíš?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.23,0:04:06.03,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki, neschudol si trochu?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.50,0:04:08.87,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,V poslednom čase pracujem dlho do noci.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.87,0:04:10.60,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah tak. Máš veľa práce.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.60,0:04:12.70,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tvoje romány sa predávajú výborne.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.10,0:04:16.30,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,V knihkupectve ich majú takúúúúto kopu!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.67,0:04:17.98,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A je na zozname bestsellerov...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.98,0:04:18.71,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prišiel si sem kvôli tejto hlúposti?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.71,0:04:20.68,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prišiel si sem kvôli tejto hlúposti?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.68,0:04:22.24,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ak nič nepotrebuješ,\Nidem spať.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.01,0:04:24.74,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžem ťa len navštíviť?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.55,0:04:27.39,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo si to potom hovoril?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.39,0:04:29.91,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pred kamerami! Že sme milenci.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.52,0:04:33.35,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I keď, bol som rád.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.23,0:04:34.99,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.53,0:04:38.50,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale teraz chce Hiro odísť z Bad Luck.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.97,0:04:44.63,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K a ostatní nás využili pre reklamu...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.17,0:04:46.80,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...a Hira to naštvalo.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.80,0:04:47.91,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To je podlosť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.91,0:04:49.97,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nemyslíš?! K je otrasný!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.48,0:04:51.46,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Myslel som oboch.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.88,0:04:54.64,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zahrávajú sa s deťmi.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.72,0:05:00.32,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ospravedlňujem sa!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.32,0:05:03.05,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Udalosti, ktoré sa odohrali v posledných dňoch...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.05,0:05:04.21,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...boli moja zodpovednosť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.76,0:05:06.22,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ano, boli.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.19,0:05:09.03,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sakano.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.03,0:05:10.15,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ano.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.63,0:05:12.89,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Som rád, že ste ich mali na starosť vy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.17,0:05:16.22,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gratulujem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.37,0:05:20.03,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tu je hodnotenie úspešnosti albumov,\Nktoré má byť zverejnené zajtra.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.21,0:05:22.40,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T-To je!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.81,0:05:28.51,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale nemôžte teraz zaváhať.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.28,0:05:31.18,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Na to, aby mohla skupina Bad Luck pokračovať...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.18,0:05:33.24,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...musíte presvedčiť Nakana, aby sa vrátil.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.85,0:05:36.91,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ano!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.93,0:05:49.06,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.55,0:06:04.74,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Si krutý.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.45,0:06:11.26,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Váš prvý album a hneď na druhom mieste.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.26,0:06:14.13,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dobrá práca! Vedel som, že to dokážeš!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.13,0:06:16.19,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale Nittle Grasper sú na prvom mieste...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.19,0:06:19.13,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...a predali 2 milióny albumov za 2 dni!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.53,0:06:21.63,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A navyše sme mali výdatnú pomoc...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.63,0:06:24.00,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...ktorá vôbec nesúvisela s našou hudbou.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.40,0:06:27.01,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Buď rád, nakoniec všetko dobre dopadlo.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.01,0:06:28.20,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Frfleš ako starý dedko!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.04,0:06:30.37,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dedko...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.81,0:06:35.30,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Možno práve kvôli tomu skončil aj Nakano!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.65,0:06:36.77,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, vidíš...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.28,0:06:40.02,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vďaka vášmu úspechu\Nna koncerte v Zepp Tokyo...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.02,0:06:43.65,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...bolo rozhodnuté, že sa vydáte\Nna turné do 30-tich miest!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.39,0:06:45.79,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30 miest?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.79,0:06:47.09,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Správne!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.09,0:06:50.26,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Od Hokkaida na severe, až po Kyushu a Okinawu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.26,0:06:51.49,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Počkaj chvíľu!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.46,0:06:55.30,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžme ísť na koncert bez Hira!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.70,0:06:58.29,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Preto ohľadom toho zvoláme\Ntlačovú konferenciu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.27,0:07:00.03,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tlačovú konferenciu?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.57,0:07:04.11,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ano. Počas ktorej oznámite svoje turné...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.11,0:07:06.77,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...a poviete, že Nakano odchádza z Bad Luck.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.85,0:07:12.18,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ako môžeš o týchto veciach rozhodovať\Nbez konzultácie s ich manažérom?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.18,0:07:14.19,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Snaď si nemyslíš,\Nže ti to všetko Touma dovolí?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.19,0:07:15.78,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bolo to jeho rozhodnutie.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.49,0:07:17.11,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čože?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.66,0:07:18.76,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tak je to.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.76,0:07:21.53,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pokiaľ je to rozhodnutie\NSeguchiho, nemáme inú možnosť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.53,0:07:23.32,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To si robíte srandu!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.59,0:07:25.10,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Som zásadne proti?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.10,0:07:27.12,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nikdy s tebou nevytvorím duo!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.43,0:07:27.97,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nikdy! Nikdy! Nikdy! Nikdy!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.97,0:07:29.16,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shindo!\NNikdy! Nikdy! Nikdy! Nikdy!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.17,0:07:31.64,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ukľudni sa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.04,0:07:35.37,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Môžem Nakana nahradiť so svojím syntetizátorom.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.71,0:07:39.80,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vieš predsa, že to dokážem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.75,0:07:49.25,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Takže Sakano,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.25,0:07:52.12,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shindo a ja pokračujeme\Ns Bad Luck...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.12,0:07:52.89,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nikdy!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.16,0:07:55.46,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bez Hira...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.86,0:07:57.69,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bez Hira to nie je možné!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.76,0:07:59.39,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.60,0:08:03.09,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo to bez Hira nie je možné?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.63,0:08:05.40,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pretože...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.14,0:08:06.90,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pretože...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.51,0:08:12.50,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pretože...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.28,0:08:21.88,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ak nemáš dôvod,\Nnie je sa o čom baviť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.25,0:08:26.12,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sakano, postaraj sa o to prosím.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.94,0:08:38.74,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.74,0:08:40.51,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eiri, čo to má znamenať?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.51,0:08:42.97,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Počula som, že si navštívil Ayaku v Kjóte.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.37,0:08:45.24,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jej otec je celý bez seba.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.24,0:08:47.55,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vraj sa jej pýtal,\Nale nechcela mu povedať...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.55,0:08:49.41,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa to deje?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.62,0:08:52.41,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eiri, počuješ ma?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.62,0:08:57.21,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo si si to zmyslel...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.92,0:09:02.36,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A teraz sa blíži našá posledná pesnička,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.36,0:09:04.76,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shindo, môžeš nám ju predstaviť?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.76,0:09:06.16,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hej...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.00,0:09:08.30,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Takže...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.30,0:09:12.70,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,následuje pesnička z nášho prvého albumu.\NDúfam, že sa vám bude páčiť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.41,0:09:15.77,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ďakujem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.48,0:09:22.17,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gratulujem!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.58,0:09:23.48,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Si úžasný.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.42,0:09:26.47,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Díkes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.56,0:09:31.35,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shuichi!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.16,0:09:36.35,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, počkaj, Shuichi!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.77,0:09:45.03,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shuichi, chceš sa hrať naháňačku?! Fajn!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.21,0:09:57.58,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shuichi!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.33,0:10:11.82,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ak budeš behať stále\Ndokola, dokola a dokola,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.00,0:10:14.83,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,osprostieš z toho!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.48,0:10:32.62,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shuichi, mám ťa!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.62,0:10:34.45,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuma, nechaj ma!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.45,0:10:36.39,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, nikdy ťa nepustím!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.39,0:10:37.79,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pusť ma prosím ťa!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.79,0:10:39.06,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, nie.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.06,0:10:40.49,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Povedal som, aby si ma pustil!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.69,0:10:44.63,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Si v poriadku?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.63,0:10:46.96,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo mi utekáš, Shuichi?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.63,0:10:51.40,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nenávidíš ma?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.77,0:10:53.86,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ja...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.24,0:10:56.26,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...nezaslúžim si byť tvojím priateľom.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.70,0:11:04.06,gravi_opening,,0000,0000,0000,,[Shikaku] = zaslúžiť, [Shika] = jeleň
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.78,0:10:59.97,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nezaslúžiš?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.38,0:11:02.51,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nezaslúžiš... nezaslúžiš... nezaslúžiš...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.91,0:11:04.02,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Takto?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.02,0:11:04.85,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuma.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.12,0:11:10.32,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dokázal by Nittle Grasper fungovať\Nbez Seguchiho, alebo Noriko?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.82,0:11:15.12,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo nemôže fungovať s inými ľuďmi?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.89,0:11:17.99,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo sa ma to pýtaš?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.36,0:11:21.76,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nemám rád, keď Shuichi\Nkladie takéto otázky.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.20,0:11:31.84,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nenávidím ťa!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.48,0:11:38.95,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}"Bad Luck\NTlačová konferencia"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.76,0:11:50.19,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Poslala ťa segra?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.90,0:11:54.69,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, neprišiel som na jej žiadosť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.10,0:11:56.79,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bola to moja vôľa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.57,0:11:59.07,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale nerozumiem tomu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.07,0:12:01.20,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayaka ťa predsa nezaujíma, alebo hej?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.87,0:12:03.27,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nestaraj sa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.71,0:12:06.20,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Napriek tomu si cestoval až do Kjóta...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.11,0:12:09.74,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo by si to robil?\NUrčite to má niečo spoločné so Shindom.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.12,0:12:15.52,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, ak ti to takto\Nvyhovuje, som len rád.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.95,0:12:20.66,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tlačová konferencia skupiny\NBad Luck práve začína.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.66,0:12:22.83,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale podľa informácii,\Nktoré sme práve dostali,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.83,0:12:24.80,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,pravdepodobne oznámia\Nodchod svojho gitaristu,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.80,0:12:27.16,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nakana Hiroshiho,\Nznámeho pod menom Hiro.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.18,0:12:43.34,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayaka...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.95,0:12:50.11,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Je pravda, že končíš s Bad Luck?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.09,0:12:55.96,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eiri mi všetko povedal.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.03,0:13:00.73,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Po pravde Shindo\Nto povedal Eirimu...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.47,0:13:04.99,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...a Eiri cestoval za mnou,\Naby mi to povedal.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.51,0:13:09.73,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím, neodchádzaj.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.11,0:13:14.67,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím ťa. Neodchádzaj z Bad Luck!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.18,0:13:21.85,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč, Ayaka.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.85,0:13:26.19,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale už som sa rozhodol.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.66,0:13:28.02,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nakano, ty...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.79,0:13:30.69,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...miluješ ma, však?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.16,0:13:37.03,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ak Bad Luck dokáže predať milión albumov,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.64,0:13:40.76,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,pôjdem s tebou na rande.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.64,0:13:48.08,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nerobím to, lebo ma o to požiadal Eiri.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.48,0:13:54.68,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chcem naňho zabudnúť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.63,0:14:05.80,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayaka...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.20,0:14:08.29,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Je čas.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.13,0:14:13.26,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shindo, nezabúdaj ako sme sa dohodli.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.87,0:14:18.84,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bude to v pohode!\NAk bude treba, postarám...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.84,0:14:19.83,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nie!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.68,0:14:22.11,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To nebude potrebné.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.95,0:14:31.18,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, počkaj, Shindo.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.56,0:14:37.62,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ďakujem, že ste si našli čas...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.33,0:14:40.59,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...a prišli na túto konferenciu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.13,0:14:43.93,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Som spevákom skupiny, Shindo Shuichi.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.93,0:14:45.46,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Moje meno je Fujisaki,\Nmám na starosti syntetizátor.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.74,0:14:48.91,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dôvod, prečo sme zvolali túto konferenciu...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.91,0:14:52.84,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...je ten, že sme sa rozhodli\Nurobiť prvé turné skupiny Bad Luck.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.68,0:14:55.77,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ohľadom Nakanovej neprítomnosti...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.18,0:14:58.11,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zúčastní sa Nakano turné spolu s vami?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.65,0:15:02.98,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Povráva sa, že Nakano odchádza\Nz Bad Luck, je to pravda?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.06,0:15:07.55,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shindo, je to pravda?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.23,0:15:09.06,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shindo!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.13,0:15:11.62,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Odpovedzte, prosím!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.96,0:15:15.47,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tak, dovolte, aby som odpovedal miesto...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.47,0:15:16.80,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Po pravde...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.84,0:15:21.56,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...chceli sme oznámiť na tejto\Nkonferencii Hirov odchod.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.97,0:15:25.17,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.61,0:15:28.24,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Predsalen... som PROTI!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.38,0:15:35.55,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lebo s Hirom sme na sebe tvrdo pracovali,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.55,0:15:37.28,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,aby sme boli ako Nittle Grasper.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.86,0:15:40.89,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro a ja sme ako slivka a kôstka,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.89,0:15:43.38,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,alebo káva a smotana.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.33,0:15:46.33,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inými slovami, vždy sme boli spolu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.33,0:15:50.00,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Napríklad na školskom festivale,\Nvždy som stresoval...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.00,0:15:51.84,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...a pesničky písal na poslednú chvíľu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.84,0:15:54.40,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Raz som kvôli rande\Nnestihol dokončiť pesničku,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.71,0:15:58.58,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,tak sme v polovici začali spievať "Furusato".
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.50,0:16:02.58,gravi_opening,,0000,0000,0000,,[furusato] - tradičná japonská pesnička
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.58,0:16:00.84,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, "Furusato" je tá pesnička:
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.28,0:16:07.15,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Usagi oishi kano yama".\NAsi tak.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.59,0:16:13.82,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale moje ciele sa postupne zmenili.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.36,0:16:16.76,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz už nechcem len\Ndosiahnuť Nittle Grasper,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.76,0:16:19.25,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ale prekonať Nittle Grasper.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.90,0:16:24.30,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale stále som nebol\Nani zďaleka tak dobrý ako Sakuma...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.70,0:16:27.04,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...a začal som byť zo seba znechutený...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.04,0:16:28.27,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shindo!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.27,0:16:29.14,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale počkať!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.91,0:16:32.07,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nie je to predsa normálne?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.54,0:16:35.03,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nemal by som na sebe začať pracovať?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.55,0:16:38.05,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Takto som začal myslieť...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.05,0:16:41.12,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...a začal som dúfať,\Nže tým uspejem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.12,0:16:43.52,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shindo, nemal by si náhodou hovoriť o Nakanovi?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.52,0:16:46.39,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Presne! Preto potrebujem Hira!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.46,0:16:49.62,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bez Hira to nepôjde!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.49,0:16:53.12,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S Hirom dokážeme prekonať Nittle Grasper!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.16,0:16:54.86,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.07,0:16:56.33,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.27,0:17:06.47,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo?!\NPretože Nittle Grasper nemá gitaristu!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.24,0:17:09.27,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tak sa vráť prosím ťa Hiro, OK?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.62,0:17:13.82,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je to za hlúpy dôvod?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.82,0:17:16.25,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To nemáte nič ako priateľstvo, dôveru...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.25,0:17:17.45,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...alebo iný psychologický dôvod?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.89,0:17:21.48,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No a čo? Nechcem do toho ísť bez Hira!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.79,0:17:24.69,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To ho nepresvedčí,\Naby sa len tak vrátil späť!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.06,0:17:27.22,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Si hlupák?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.20,0:17:38.20,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Musím uznať, presvedčil si ma!\NTotálne si ma presvedčil!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.18,0:17:40.30,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.05,0:17:50.18,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Priateľ!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.72,0:17:52.21,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tvoj sen je môj sen!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.72,0:17:54.45,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A tvoj sen je môj sen!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.33,0:17:57.45,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Poďme do toho spolu\Na získajme ten milión!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.03,0:18:05.90,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Priateľ!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.14,0:18:10.41,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, hej, len prosím pracujte...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.41,0:18:12.67,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...a dúfajte v svoj milión, alebo dva.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.24,0:18:14.71,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,V prvom rade jeden milión!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.71,0:18:16.37,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre, tak jeden milión, jeden!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.88,0:18:19.82,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Presne! Jeden milión kópii je náš cieľ!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.82,0:18:20.75,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Už nie je!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.99,0:18:29.22,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuma!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.93,0:18:33.10,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gratulujem, predali ste\Nmilión svojích albumov!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.50,0:18:35.97,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A tu je darček od Tohmi.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.47,0:18:37.59,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.10,0:18:39.74,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jeden milión? Skutočne?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.74,0:18:40.70,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hej!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.70,0:18:43.04,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A darček vám predávam ja,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.04,0:18:44.97,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,takže je to extra-prekvapenie, Shuichi!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.08,0:18:54.88,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ak by chcel gitaristu,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.05,0:18:58.99,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,mohli sme mu dať\Nnajlepších z N-G.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.49,0:19:03.22,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Na tom im nezáleží.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.23,0:19:09.16,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bez ohľadu na to, čo sa okolo\Nnich deje, vždy skončia spolu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.40,0:19:13.03,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ty vieš tuším všetko.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.44,0:19:15.37,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale nerád vidím...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.37,0:19:17.77,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...ako ťa Shindo neustále ovplyvňuje.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.58,0:19:28.49,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo ti je, Eiri?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.49,0:19:29.47,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eiri?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.40,0:19:39.38,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eiri...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.60,0:19:47.76,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuma!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.44,0:19:52.74,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je, Shuichi?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.08,0:19:54.14,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ospravedlňujem sa!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.71,0:19:58.01,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Za tie divné veci, ktoré som vtedy vravel...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.68,0:19:59.98,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Divné veci?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.45,0:20:03.18,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Divné veci... Divné veci... Divné veci...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.62,0:20:07.18,gravi_opening,,0000,0000,0000,,[Koto] = japonský hudobný nástroj
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.62,0:20:05.59,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Toto je divná "Koto".
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.06,0:20:10.86,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ak si nespomínaš, tak nevadí.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.70,0:20:14.10,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale viackrát už nezaváham.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.06,0:20:46.36,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Amidst a noisy crowd of people
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.06,0:20:46.36,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nigiyaka na hitogomi ni
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.80,0:20:51.10,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The murmured words melt away
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.80,0:20:51.10,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tokeru tsubuyaki ga
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.50,0:20:55.63,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Scattered at my feet
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.50,0:20:55.63,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ashimoto ni chirabatta
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.71,0:21:00.23,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are memories that become blurred by it
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.71,0:21:00.23,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Omoide nijimaseru
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.71,0:21:06.25,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wander aimlessly
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.71,0:21:06.25,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mayoi aruku
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.25,0:21:09.84,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And the brilliant lights of the town
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.25,0:21:09.84,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Machi no kagayaki wa
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.09,0:21:13.45,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Glaring one way
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.39,0:21:19.02,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Illuminate me, on the verge of freezing
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.39,0:21:19.02,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kogoesou na boku o terasu
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.06,0:21:26.04,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The cold time brings dreams from the skies
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.06,0:21:26.04,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumetai toki ga yume o furaseru
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.04,0:21:30.71,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And they slip through my fingers
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.04,0:21:30.71,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kono te no naka o surinukete
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.71,0:21:35.48,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Counting my wishes, when I wake up
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.71,0:21:35.48,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Negai kazoe mezameta toki ni
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.48,0:21:43.52,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You are there in the wavering vision
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.48,0:21:43.52,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yureru maboroshi ni kimi ga utsuru
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.52,0:21:49.15,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A faint silhouette that guides me
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.52,0:21:49.15,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Boku o michibiku kasuka na shiruetto
